Packages 
Package Description
controller
This package contains the various controller level classes used by the system All controllers acquire information from the FrontController class
databases
This package contains the various classes used for the storage, retrieval, and management of data used by our system
entity.art
This package contains the art entity class
entity.markets
This package contains the Wallet entity class
entity.user
This package contains the various types of User entities that exist in the system
exceptions.market
This package contains exceptions associated with the market functionalities
exceptions.user
This package contains the exceptions associated with the user management system
interfaces
This package contains the interfaces used by some entity classes
usecases.art
This package contains usecase level classes used for interacting with Art entities Note: The Appraiser is not implemented and remain unused as of Phase 1.
usecases.markets
This package contains usecase level classes used for interacting with market related entities
usecases.user
This package contains usecase level classes used for interacting with user related entities
utils
This package contains miscellaneous classes that provided utility elsewhere in the application
view
This package contains presenter (View) classes who are responsible for displaying information to the user
